text: Iltebanovo () is a rural locality (a selo) in Kunakbayevsky Selsoviet, Uchalinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 480 as of 2010. There are 18 streets. == Geography == It is located 10 km from Uchaly, 2 km from Kunakbayevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Uchalinsky District
title: Iltebanovo
